# ShakespeareCRM — example SPARQL queries (Phase 0 targets)
#
# Prefixes MUST be aligned with generated ontology and data load scripts.
# Placeholder prefixes below — replace after LinkML/Oxigraph import:
#
# PREFIX crm: <http://www.cidoc-crm.org/cidoc-crm/>
# PREFIX sc:  <https://example.org/shakespeare-crm/>
#
# Named graphs: use GRAPH ?g { ... } once graph IRIs are fixed in Phase 0.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Q1 — Betrayal events and participating characters (CRM event-centric)
